# Demo Builder -- KS Global Estates

## Status: COMPLETE

Hero feature delivered: full split-pane luxury real estate platform with Leaflet world map, 25-property mock DB, price-pin markers, 6-dimension filter panel, detail drawer with gallery + inquiry form, and persisted favorites.

## Build summary

- **Hero feature:** Leaflet world map (zoom 3, global spread) with custom price-pin DivIcon markers (gold = active, ink = default), flyTo on selection, synchronized property list with card-scroll. Filter panel: type, status, price preset pills, beds, baths, region, text search, sort. Detail slide-in panel: gallery carousel with thumbnails, features list, inquiry form. Favorites: heart per card + localStorage persistence + dedicated Saved view.
- **Local preview URL:** `http://localhost:4090/` (serve `public/demos/ks-global-estates/`)
- **Files touched:** 16 (14 new source files, 2 site files -- workSamples.js entry + screenshot)
- **`npm run build` (demo-src):** PASS (503ms)
- **`npm run build` (michaelwegter.com):** PASS (5.67s)
- **Backend touched:** No
- **Dash gate:** PASS -- no em/en dashes in source or built output
- **Screenshot:** `public/work-samples/ks-global-estates.png` captured

## Design decisions

- Cormorant Garamond 400 (not 300 -- avoids thin-render on Windows as warned) + DM Sans
- Palette: ink/canvas/gold/mid (as locked in pre-researcher)
- CartoDB Voyager tiles: clean, editorial, suits luxury brand
- Filter uses price preset pills (not range slider) -- mobile-friendly as recommended for touch
- Property detail slides in from right (not a centered modal) -- editorial pattern
- No AI-tell patterns: no blob dividers, no Inter-only font, no uniform grid, no frosted glass on everything

