## handoff

- **Produced:** Full Vite/React demo built and deployed to `public/demos/ks-global-estates/`; workSamples.js entry (id: 11) inserted; screenshot captured; `build-report.md` written.
- **Decisions:** Frontend-only (no backend needed); price preset pills over slider (mobile UX); Cormorant 400 not 300 (Windows render); CartoDB Voyager tiles; detail slides in from right.
- **Next needs:** CEO review (`build-ceo.out`), then cover letter writer. Demo link is `/demos/ks-global-estates/`. No credentials needed (all mock data).
- **Risks:** Leaflet markers overlap at zoom 3 for same-city pairs (Dubai, London, NYC) -- mitigated by lat/lng jitter per researcher spec. Unsplash images load from CDN; offline QA will show placeholder only if Unsplash blocks.
- **Build gate:** Both `npm run build` passes confirmed. Dash gate clean. Site entry valid.
